# Job Artifact Privacy

- Do not commit sensitive personal details unless explicitly approved.
- Keep recruiter names, compensation specifics, and personal identifiers sanitized in versioned docs.
- Prefer placeholders or generalized references for private data.
- If uncertain whether data is sensitive, ask before writing it.
- When creating examples, default to sanitized, reusable variants.
